## Key Decisions
- **OB secondary fetch over request expansion**: chose `Promise.all` of detail calls per product over attempting to expand the product search payload — proven reliable and matches what the OB portal does.
- **`InvestorDscr` (no hyphen) for DSCR**: OB rejects `Investor-DSCR`; probed 60+ enum variants — only `FullDoc | WrittenVOE | Stated | NoIncomeVerification | InvestorDscr | InvestorDSCR` are accepted on channel 165481. Alt-doc (bank stmt, VOE, asset, tax) all routes to `WrittenVOE`.
- **ENCOMPASS_* prefix with legacy fallback**: API handlers read `ENCOMPASS_*` first, fall back to unprefixed names so old Vercel env doesn't break existing deploys.
- **PDF server-side via pdf-lib**: avoids client-side dep bloat; Resend `attachments[]` expects base64 content.
- **Lock-period filter in parseOBResponse**: OB returns same rate at 30/45/60-day locks with different prices — filter to the user's `desiredLockPeriod`; fall back to nearest available lock if none match exactly.

