## OB Request Shape (DSCR Reference)
Key non-obvious values that make DSCR return products on channel 165481:
```
loanInformation.automatedUnderwritingSystem = 'ManualTraditional'
loanInformation.includeLOCompensationInPricing = 'NoBuyerPaid'
loanInformation.dutyToServe = 'No'
loanInformation.missionScore = 'Zero'
loanInformation.customFields = [
  { customFieldInputName: 'CustomProductFilter01', customFieldValue: '110', columnName: 'CustomLenderField4' },
  { customFieldInputName: 'CustomProductFilter02', customFieldValue: '110', columnName: 'CustomLenderField5' },
  { customFieldInputName: 'CustomProductFilter03', customFieldValue: '110', columnName: 'CustomLenderField7' },
  { customFieldInputName: 'CustomProductFilter04', customFieldValue: '110', columnName: 'CustomLenderField8' },
]
loanInformation.expandedGuidelines.incomeVerificationType = 'InvestorDscr'
loanInformation.expandedGuidelines.debtServiceCoverageRatio = <ratio>
```

